snippet.title: Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 | Coming Soon | @hotstarOfficial
snippet.description:
Zindagi badi ajeeb hai...
#hotstarspecials  #TaazaKhabar Season 2 coming soon only on @hotstarOfficial 

Watch #HotstarSpecials Taaza Khabar only on Disney+ Hotstar: http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

#TaazaKhabarOnHotstar #BhuvanBam #ShriyaPilgaonkar @BBKVProductions

--

With good Karma on one’s side, can one man set out to become a master of his own destiny? 

Disney+ Hotstar’s upcoming fantasy-drama series, Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar explores just this with the one of India’s most beloved content creator, Bhuvan Bam in the lead. Set in Mumbai, this one-of-a-kind uplifting series will take viewers on a riveting ride of a man stumbling upon a miracle and the ripples it creates in his humble life. 

The series is being directed by Himank Gaur  produced by Rohit Raj under the banner of BB Ki Vines Productions. The show has been penned by powerful writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal and also stars Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Deven Bhojani, Prathmesh Parab and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.
 
The resounding success of Taaza Khabhar season 1 is a testament to Disney+ Hotstar’s commitment in its pursuit of bringing quality entertainment. The heartfelt response and immense love "Taaza Khabar" received from you all have been overwhelming. It's been a testament to the power of storytelling, the dedication of our talented cast who brought this unique tale to life. The success of the first season was marked by it being the 3rd most watched show on OTT with over 30 million viewers!

Our team is reuniting to delve deeper into the extraordinary world we've created, promising to bring you a season that's as enchanting and engaging as the first. This journey, from the inception of the first season to the anticipation of the next, has been incredible, and it's all thanks to your support and love.

Instagram► https://www.instagram.com/bhuvan.bam22/           
Facebook► https://www.facebook.com/BBkiVines/
Twitter►https://twitter.com/Bhuvan_Bam

Follow  @BBKVProductions   for BTS & more updates.

#TaazaKhabarOnHotstar #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

Bhuvan Bam is a comedian, singer-songwriter, actor and entrepreneur. He created the entire universe of BB Ki Vines, a content power house, to see more of his content follow him on

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 41 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 5th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

snippet.title: #Video | काला चश्मा लगा लीजिए | Neelkamal Singh | Mahima Gupta | New Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
ढोल ताशे के साथ तैयार हो जाई काहेकी #NeelkamalSingh फिर से तहलका मचाने आ गए अपने काले काले
चश्मे वाले गाने के साथ | 

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs: @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Credits:
Title - Kala Chashma Laga Lijiye
Hindi - काला चश्मा लगा लीजिए
Singer - Neelkamal Singh
Feat - Mahima Gupta
Lyrics - Ashutosh Tiwari
Music - Shubham Raj (SBR)

Video director & choreographer - Lakkie vishwakarma 
DOP - Yogesh Singh 
Edit - Rishu singh 
Assistant -Suresh & Ashu 
Di - Rohit singh 
Production - Aakash Vishwakarma 
Art - Raja

Lyrics:

आँखों ही आँखों मे आँखे चार होता है
दे दे दिल जो वही,दिलदार होता है
अपने सनम को,प्यार से हमको थोड़ा देखा कीजिये
रूप है धूप है,काले आँखों मे तो चश्मा लगा लीजिए...
ऐ मेरे हमसफ़र,जरा आँखों मे तो चश्मा लगा लीजिये

गाल गुलाब के पंख के जैसे,होंठ तेरे मधुशाला है
कह दो सभी से की आज अभी से आपका ये दिलवाला है
ऐसे हँस के,दिल मे बस के,
जरा सीने में तो चाहत जगा लीजिये
रूप है धूप है,काले आँखों मे तो चश्मा लगा लीजिए...

हुस्न की रानी, तू मस्तानी,मौसम की बाहार है तू
ताजमहल सी,कोई गजल सी,नीलकमल की प्यार है तू
(तेरा दीवाना मैं मस्ताना)
ओ मेरी जाने जा..आएगा मजा,
मेरे मीत यह गीत गुनगुना लीजिये
रूप है धूप है,काले आँखों मे तो चश्मा लगा लीजिए...

#KalaChashmaLagaLijiye
#neelkamalsingh 
#saregamahumbhojpuri

snippet.description:
Topics Covered In Video-
1) WWE Wrestlemania 40 highlights & full show results in Hindi
2) Roman Reigns speared The Rock at Wrestlemania 40
3) Cody Rhodes lost sitting in the ring
4) Roman Reigns & The Rock won against Cody Rhodes & Seth Rollins
5) Sami Zayn wins Intercontinental Championship
6) WWE Wrestlemania 40 results
7) The Rock entrance Wrestlemania 40

#wrestlemania #wwe #therock #romanreigns 

'Thoka Rock-Roman Ne🤯' Bloodline Rules, The Rock & Roman Reigns - WWE Wrestlemania 40 Highlights

WrestleMania 40, the pinnacle of sports entertainment, delivered a night of electrifying highlights that will be etched in WWE history. The event was marked by the highly anticipated clash between two icons, Roman Reigns and The Rock. In a moment of sheer intensity, Reigns unleashed his devastating Spear, crashing into The Rock with unparalleled force. However, The Rock retaliated with his signature move, the Rock Bottom, delivering a crushing blow to Cody Rhodes. The match between Reigns & The Rock and Cody Rhodes & Seth Rollins was a spectacle of raw power and unmatched skill. As WrestleMania 40 unfolded, fans were treated to a full show of jaw-dropping moments, showcasing the very best of WWE. With legends like The Rock and Reigns at the forefront, WrestleMania 40 proved once again why it is the grandest stage of them all.

00:00 Jawaan The Rock
00:30 Rhea Ripley Vs Becky Lynch Women’s World Championship
01:51 Undisputed Tag Team Championship 6 pack ladder match
03:47 Rey Mysterio & Andrade Vs Domink Mysterio & Santos Escobar
04:38 Jey Uso Vs Jimmy Uso
06:45 What an entrance
07:34 Sami Zayn Vs Gunther Intercontinental Championship
09:50 The Rock & Roman Reigns Vs Cody Rhodes & Seth Rollins

snippet.title: New Ather Rizta Family Scooter Walkaround | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Ather today launched their family scooter Rizta at a starting price of Rs 1,09,999, Rizta was launched alongside Ather Stack 6 and their helmet lineup called Halo. In this video, I have covered both Rizta and Halo. However, I will reserve my comments on whether this is a family scooter until I ride it. 


Transparency Note:
This video was recorded at some events like Auto Expo, where dealers or manufacturers showcase their cars. While the car belongs to the manufacturer and permissions might be required in order to record or film it, there is no financial transaction done between the manufacturer and us or anyone related. All the costs of Travel, Shoot, Stay, etc, are borne by Team Gagan Choudhary or GaadiFy. Neither the owner of the vehicle or the organiser of the event gets to see the video or alter it after or before publishing it.

snippet.title: ସୁନୟନା | SUNAYANA | Full Episode 44 | New Odia Mega Serial on Sidharth TV @7.30PM
snippet.description:
“ସୁନୟନା” ଆଜି ସନ୍ଧ୍ୟା ୭ଟା ୩୦ ରେ ... ସିଦ୍ଧାର୍ଥ TVରେ... 
ଆମ ହସକୁରି ସୁନା ଝିଅ ସୁନୟନା - ପାଠ ସିନା ଟିକେ କମ ହେଲେ ମନରେ ତାର ଅସୁମାରୀ ସ୍ବପ୍ନ - ସିଏ କଣ ପାଇପାରିବ ତାର ସ୍ବପ୍ନର ରାଜକୁମାର ? ସିଏ କଣ ସମସ୍ତଙ୍କୁ ଖୁସିରେ ରଖିପାରିବ ? 
What happens when a girl who is unable to get married, is sought after by a family of repute happily accepted the girl as the daughter in law. Seeing their ideology on promoting women empowerment, the girl is hopeful that she will fulfil her ambition of learning to speak English but she discovers that the family she is married into has ulterior motives. Watch this powerful serial SUNAYANA @7.30PM - Only on Sidharth TV

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4052 | 6 April 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4052: Electrician Jethalal
--------------------------------------------------------
Abdul brings a new fan for his shop so that Jethalal and his friends can sit comfortably in the summer. Babita calls Iyer and complains about a fault in their AC. Jethalal offers to fix the AC when Iyer is unable to find a mechanic. Will he be able to fix the AC?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4052, 6 April 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000271223

snippet.title: Jethalal क्यों गया Terrace पर सोने? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Adventure With Tapu Sena
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Now that the oath's secret is known, Daya calls her mother to decide what to do next. Daya cuts off the phone and lets Jethalal know that while the oath can go on, he should stop using the fan going forward. After hearing everything, Jethalal chooses to keep taking the pledge in hopes of Tapu's success. Will Tapu's success be ensured by Jethalal's suffering? View the episode to learn more.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1696
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Vineeth Sreenivasan - Dhyan Interview | Varshangalkku Shesham | Visakh Subramaniam | Pranav Mohanlal
snippet.description:
Vineeth Sreenivasan - Dhyan Interview | Varshangalkku Shesham | Visakh Subramaniam | Pranav Mohanlal | Part 02

Varshangalkku Shesham is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language period satirical drama film written and directed by Vineeth Sreenivasan. It was produced and distributed by Visakh Subramaniam for Merryland Cinemas. The film stars Pranav Mohanlal, Dhyan Sreenivasan, Nivin Pauly, Vineeth Sreenivasan, Basil Joseph, Aju Varghese, Neeraj Madhav, Kalyani Priyadarshan, Neeta Pillai, Arjun Lal, Nikhil Nair, Shaan Rahman. The film's original score and songs were composed by debutant Amrit Ramnath.

It revolves around two young men who leave their hometown in Kerala to chase their dream of becoming big in the cinema-obsessed world of Kodambakkam, Madras, the cinema-hub of the 1970's and 80's South Indian cinema. Principal photography that began on 26 October 2023 and was completed on 20 December 2023. It is scheduled to be released in theatres worldwide on 11 April 2024.

The film follows Venu (Dhyan Sreenivasan) and Murali s'(Pranav Mohanlal) journey from his Kerala hometown to pursue his cinematic dreams in the cinema-centric landscape of Madras, now Chennai.

The film have an ensemble star cast, led by Pranav Mohanlal, Dhyan Sreenivasan, Aju Varghese, Kalyani Priyadarshan, Basil Joseph, Vineeth, Neeraj Madhav, Neeta Pillai, Arjun Lal, Nikhil Nair, Shaan Rahman, and Nivin Pauly.  Dhyan lost body weight to prepare for his role. The film also marks the fifth reunion of Nivin and Vineeth.

snippet.title: Kunafa Recipe in Tamil | Turkish Sweet Recipe in Tamil | Homemade Kunafa Semiya
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make kunafa recipe in Tamil. This kunafa recipe is a very popular turkish dessert recipe and in this recipe we are going to make the kunafa semiya at home. Traditionally cheese is used in making the recipe but I have made this version without cheese to use readily available ingredients. 
#kunafa #kunafarecipe #turkishrecipeintamil

Friends, please do try this kunafa recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!


Ingredients to make Kunafa without Cheese:
For the Homemade Kunafa semiya
1 cup Maida
1/2 cup Corn flour
2 tbsp Oil
pinch of Salt
required Water

For the Cream Filling without Cheese:
3 tbsp Corn flour
2 tbsp Sugar
1.5 cup Water
1 tbsp Butter
pinch of Cardamom powder

For sugar syrup:
1 cup Sugar
1 cup Water
pinch of Cardamom
10 drops of Lemon juice

Ingredients to make Kunafa with store-bought Kunfa dough :
200 g Kunafa semiya
100g Butter
150g Mozzarella cheese
For sugar syrup:
1 cup Sugar
1 cup Water
pinch of Cardamom
10 drops of Lemon juice

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4051 | 5 April 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4051: AC On Or Off?
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha informs Jethalal that a company is coming to meet him for the launch of a new product. Jethalal disturbs Champaklal and Tapu's sleep, as Tapu prefers sleeping with the AC on while Champaklal is not comfortable with it.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4051, 5 April 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000271073

snippet.title: Vineeth Sreenivasan - Dhyan Interview | Varshangalkku Shesham |Visakh Subramaniam | Pranav Mohanlal
snippet.description:
Vineeth Sreenivasan - Dhyan Interview | Varshangalkku Shesham | Visakh Subramaniam | Pranav Mohanlal 

Varshangalkku Shesham is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language period satirical drama film written and directed by Vineeth Sreenivasan. It was produced and distributed by Visakh Subramaniam for Merryland Cinemas. The film stars Pranav Mohanlal, Dhyan Sreenivasan, Nivin Pauly, Vineeth Sreenivasan, Basil Joseph, Aju Varghese, Neeraj Madhav, Kalyani Priyadarshan, Neeta Pillai, Arjun Lal, Nikhil Nair, Shaan Rahman. The film's original score and songs were composed by debutant Amrit Ramnath.

It revolves around two young men who leave their hometown in Kerala to chase their dream of becoming big in the cinema-obsessed world of Kodambakkam, Madras, the cinema-hub of the 1970's and 80's South Indian cinema. Principal photography that began on 26 October 2023 and was completed on 20 December 2023. It is scheduled to be released in theatres worldwide on 11 April 2024.

The film follows Venu (Dhyan Sreenivasan) and Murali s'(Pranav Mohanlal) journey from his Kerala hometown to pursue his cinematic dreams in the cinema-centric landscape of Madras, now Chennai.

The film have an ensemble star cast, led by Pranav Mohanlal, Dhyan Sreenivasan, Aju Varghese, Kalyani Priyadarshan, Basil Joseph, Vineeth, Neeraj Madhav, Neeta Pillai, Arjun Lal, Nikhil Nair, Shaan Rahman, and Nivin Pauly.  Dhyan lost body weight to prepare for his role. The film also marks the fifth reunion of Nivin and Vineeth.

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: ସୁନୟନା | SUNAYANA | Full Episode 43 | New Odia Mega Serial on Sidharth TV @7.30PM
snippet.description:
“ସୁନୟନା” ଆଜି ସନ୍ଧ୍ୟା ୭ଟା ୩୦ ରେ ... ସିଦ୍ଧାର୍ଥ TVରେ... 
ଆମ ହସକୁରି ସୁନା ଝିଅ ସୁନୟନା - ପାଠ ସିନା ଟିକେ କମ ହେଲେ ମନରେ ତାର ଅସୁମାରୀ ସ୍ବପ୍ନ - ସିଏ କଣ ପାଇପାରିବ ତାର ସ୍ବପ୍ନର ରାଜକୁମାର ? ସିଏ କଣ ସମସ୍ତଙ୍କୁ ଖୁସିରେ ରଖିପାରିବ ? 
What happens when a girl who is unable to get married, is sought after by a family of repute happily accepted the girl as the daughter in law. snippet.description:

Khumar Episode 40 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 4th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir

Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya

Episode 4050: Prank Ulta Padh Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Mahila Mandal and Champaklal reveal that their drunken behavior was just an act to prank Purush Mandli, leaving Popatlal unaware. Afterwards, Purush Mandli gathers for soda and a discussion on global warming.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
